578
00:24:10,126 --> 00:24:10,926
Then the house will be yours.

579
00:24:18,446 --> 00:24:18,846
Sign it then.

580
00:24:27,920 --> 00:24:35,750
(Seller: Hong Jinkui) (Buyer: Yu Ming)

581
00:24:38,005 --> 00:24:38,285
Bro.

582
00:24:38,926 --> 00:24:39,646
Do you think this time

583
00:24:39,646 --> 00:24:40,646
we can get our money back?

584
00:24:41,085 --> 00:24:42,005
My great-grandma said

585
00:24:42,245 --> 00:24:42,886
no problem.

586
00:24:43,206 --> 00:24:43,966
We'll definitely get it back.

587
00:24:44,406 --> 00:24:45,005
Forget it, man.

588
00:24:45,886 --> 00:24:47,045
If your great-grandma weren't sick,

589
00:24:47,525 --> 00:24:48,045
you wouldn't

590
00:24:48,045 --> 00:24:48,926
have told us today

591
00:24:49,166 --> 00:24:49,646
that Hu Deshuai

592
00:24:49,646 --> 00:24:50,805
hid the money inside the villa wall.

593
00:24:52,525 --> 00:24:53,485
You don't know what kind

594
00:24:53,485 --> 00:24:54,285
of person Hu Deshuai is?

595
00:24:55,525 --> 00:24:56,765
Back then, he said he knew us.

596
00:24:57,126 --> 00:24:58,005
Said we built walls for him,

597
00:24:59,045 --> 00:25:00,245
He even knew where we lived.

598
00:25:00,525 --> 00:25:01,245
He told me

599
00:25:01,525 --> 00:25:02,565
if I told anyone about it,

600
00:25:02,646 --> 00:25:03,686
he'd kill my whole family.

601
00:25:04,005 --> 00:25:04,805
Bullshit.

602
00:25:05,085 --> 00:25:05,886
Kill our whole family?

603
00:25:06,005 --> 00:25:06,646
How dare he?

604
00:25:06,846 --> 00:25:07,966
That's just like you.

605
00:25:07,966 --> 00:25:09,045
Alright, alright.

606
00:25:09,085 --> 00:25:09,606
Stop rambling.

607
00:25:10,005 --> 00:25:10,686
Let's go take a look first.

608
00:25:16,446 --> 00:25:17,005
This way.

609
00:25:19,366 --> 00:25:19,926
What are you doing?

610
00:25:20,446 --> 00:25:21,166
You can't just come in here.

611
00:25:21,406 --> 00:25:21,686
Leave.

612
00:25:22,325 --> 00:25:22,886
Well...

613
00:25:23,325 --> 00:25:25,045
I built this place.
I just wanted to have a look.

614
00:25:25,406 --> 00:25:26,686
Leave. Stop wasting my time.

615
00:25:29,485 --> 00:25:30,166
What's with that attitude?

616
00:25:31,886 --> 00:25:32,085
Let's go.

617
00:25:35,846 --> 00:25:36,446
Bad attitude.

618
00:25:54,900 --> 00:25:58,550
(Certificate of Real Estate Ownership)

619
00:26:26,805 --> 00:26:27,366
Hello.

620
00:26:28,966 --> 00:26:29,446
Hello.

621
00:26:29,646 --> 00:26:31,206
Are you the new owner?

622
00:26:31,686 --> 00:26:32,366
Yes, yes.

623
00:26:34,406 --> 00:26:35,206
You've already moved in?

624
00:26:35,565 --> 00:26:36,085
No, not yet.

625
00:26:36,166 --> 00:26:37,686
The place isn't ready.

626
00:26:38,926 --> 00:26:40,646
I'm the security team leader

627
00:26:40,765 --> 00:26:41,325
here at Ziyu Garden.

628
00:26:41,606 --> 00:26:42,366
My name is Zhan Chun.

629
00:26:42,525 --> 00:26:43,366
Nice to meet you.

630
00:26:43,366 --> 00:26:43,646
Yeah.

631
00:26:43,886 --> 00:26:45,005
I just came by

632
00:26:45,005 --> 00:26:45,886
to see if you needed

633
00:26:46,005 --> 00:26:46,325
anything.

634
00:26:47,646 --> 00:26:48,406
Actually,

635
00:26:48,406 --> 00:26:49,525
I've got a lot of construction debris.

636
00:26:49,525 --> 00:26:50,725
Could you help me clear it out?

637
00:26:51,045 --> 00:26:52,045
Construction debris? We...

638
00:26:52,406 --> 00:26:53,686
don't offer that service.

639
00:26:54,245 --> 00:26:54,725
But no problem.

640
00:26:54,725 --> 00:26:55,686
I can check around for you.

641
00:26:55,966 --> 00:26:57,005
Great! Thank you.

642
00:26:57,206 --> 00:26:57,606
It's okay.

643
00:26:57,725 --> 00:26:58,765
I'll come find you

644
00:26:58,765 --> 00:26:59,406
once I've arranged it.

645
00:26:59,525 --> 00:26:59,926
Great!

646
00:27:00,206 --> 00:27:00,565
Great!

647
00:27:00,725 --> 00:27:01,085
Great!

648
00:27:01,406 --> 00:27:01,646
Great!

649
00:27:02,406 --> 00:27:02,926
Alright, then.

650
00:27:03,126 --> 00:27:03,446
Goodbye.

651
00:27:04,005 --> 00:27:04,686
Congrats on moving in.

652
00:27:37,760 --> 00:27:40,230
(Chongqing Noodles)

653
00:27:47,926 --> 00:27:48,606
Unit 505 has a new owner.

654
00:27:50,606 --> 00:27:51,565
He moved in this morning.

655
00:27:57,406 --> 00:27:58,166
What should we do?

656
00:27:59,765 --> 00:28:01,166
Figure out what we can do. What else?

657
00:28:06,045 --> 00:28:06,485
Those three guys

658
00:28:07,005 --> 00:28:07,725
knew Hu Deshuai.

659
00:28:08,646 --> 00:28:09,045
Who?

660
00:28:10,525 --> 00:28:11,366
Hu Deshuai.

661
00:28:20,525 --> 00:28:21,366
Bro, I'm still hungry.

662
00:28:21,805 --> 00:28:22,325
I want another bowl.

663
00:28:22,485 --> 00:28:23,485
Why don't you eat the bowl, too?

664
00:28:23,646 --> 00:28:24,565
We haven't got the money back,

665
00:28:24,725 --> 00:28:25,725
and you are eating me into poverty.

666
00:28:27,085 --> 00:28:27,446
Listen.

667
00:28:27,805 --> 00:28:28,126
Tomorrow,

668
00:28:28,285 --> 00:28:29,525
grab your tools

669
00:28:29,765 --> 00:28:30,565
and go find a job.

670
00:28:30,846 --> 00:28:32,126
Every debt has its debtor.

671
00:28:32,485 --> 00:28:33,166
Why don't we go see

672
00:28:33,166 --> 00:28:34,166
if Hu Deshuai's company

673
00:28:34,166 --> 00:28:35,005
is still around?

674
00:28:35,005 --> 00:28:36,606
Hu Deshuai's been dead for years.

675
00:28:37,166 --> 00:28:38,166
No one is there.

676
00:28:38,366 --> 00:28:39,485
How did Hu Deshuai

677
00:28:39,485 --> 00:28:40,206
die, anyway?

678
00:28:40,846 --> 00:28:41,206
No idea.

679
00:28:41,966 --> 00:28:43,446
I heard someone killed him

680
00:28:43,446 --> 00:28:44,206
and dumped him in the sea.

681
00:28:44,325 --> 00:28:45,325
Alright, alright. That's enough.

682
00:28:45,325 --> 00:28:45,926
Stop talking.

683
00:28:46,166 --> 00:28:46,725
Get some of this.

684
00:28:52,446 --> 00:28:52,846
Ma'am,

685
00:28:53,045 --> 00:28:53,725
can I get another serving?

686
00:28:54,765 --> 00:28:54,966
Sure.

687
00:28:55,686 --> 00:28:56,005
No problem.

688
00:29:19,166 --> 00:29:19,725
Chun?

689
00:29:20,765 --> 00:29:21,606
You don't remember me?

690
00:29:24,045 --> 00:29:24,606
Tiechui!

691
00:29:26,686 --> 00:29:27,926
Look... who he is.

692
00:29:28,285 --> 00:29:29,765
What a small world!

693
00:29:30,245 --> 00:29:30,606
Me.

694
00:29:31,325 --> 00:29:31,846
Tiezhu.

695
00:29:32,325 --> 00:29:33,085
The foreman.

696
00:29:33,366 --> 00:29:33,725
Yeah.

697
00:29:33,926 --> 00:29:34,606
I remember.

698
00:29:35,045 --> 00:29:35,366
Right?

699
00:29:35,406 --> 00:29:35,725
Right?

700
00:29:35,926 --> 00:29:36,765
It's been years.

701
00:29:38,126 --> 00:29:39,406
You're doing pretty well now.

702
00:29:40,285 --> 00:29:40,765
Civil servant?

703
00:29:40,966 --> 00:29:42,126
No, don't talk nonsense.

704
00:29:42,686 --> 00:29:43,886
I'm a security guard now.

705
00:29:45,166 --> 00:29:45,525
Guard?

706
00:29:45,525 --> 00:29:46,206
Not a driver any more?

707
00:29:46,325 --> 00:29:46,606
No.

708
00:29:46,606 --> 00:29:47,206
I changed careers.

709
00:29:47,485 --> 00:29:48,406
This restaurant is mine.

710
00:29:48,406 --> 00:29:49,126
My wife and I run it.

711
00:29:49,126 --> 00:29:49,646
This is my wife.

712
00:29:50,725 --> 00:29:51,285
Nice to meet you.

713
00:29:51,285 --> 00:29:51,725
Hello.

714
00:29:53,045 --> 00:29:53,686
What brings

715
00:29:54,406 --> 00:29:54,886
you guys here?

716
00:29:55,166 --> 00:29:55,686
Collecting money.

717
00:29:57,606 --> 00:29:58,406
Hu Deshuai owes

718
00:29:58,446 --> 00:29:59,805
the wages of 133 workers.

719
00:30:00,085 --> 00:30:01,045
He never paid us.

720
00:30:01,525 --> 00:30:02,446
He owed me money, too.

721
00:30:02,646 --> 00:30:03,525
How much does he owe you?

722
00:30:03,805 --> 00:30:04,406
Two million.

723
00:30:05,166 --> 00:30:06,325
You know he's dead, right?

724
00:30:06,525 --> 00:30:06,966
Yeah.

725
00:30:07,406 --> 00:30:08,045
What're you going to do?

726
00:30:08,045 --> 00:30:09,206
Sometimes we have to accept bad luck.

727
00:30:09,206 --> 00:30:09,966
That's what I did.

728
00:30:10,085 --> 00:30:10,966
Listen to me, go home.

729
00:30:11,245 --> 00:30:12,166
No way.

730
00:30:12,285 --> 00:30:13,005
If I can't get the money,

731
00:30:13,406 --> 00:30:14,166
I'm not going home.

732
00:30:14,325 --> 00:30:14,765
What else

733
00:30:14,765 --> 00:30:15,525
can you do then?

734
00:30:15,525 --> 00:30:16,245
Who can you ask for it?

735
00:30:16,485 --> 00:30:17,325
When we were building

736
00:30:17,525 --> 00:30:18,565
Ziyu Garden,

737
00:30:19,085 --> 00:30:19,765
I went to the bathroom

738
00:30:20,485 --> 00:30:21,126
and I saw Hu Deshuai...

739
00:30:21,166 --> 00:30:21,805
San.

740
00:30:22,206 --> 00:30:22,765
Hey, um...

741
00:30:22,846 --> 00:30:23,725
Weren't you still hungry?

742
00:30:23,725 --> 00:30:24,886
Then eat my portion.

743
00:30:28,045 --> 00:30:28,926
I... I'll eat first.

744
00:30:29,485 --> 00:30:30,206
Okay.

745
00:30:30,245 --> 00:30:31,565
Take your time.

746
00:30:35,525 --> 00:30:36,406
I'm working

747
00:30:36,406 --> 00:30:37,485
as a security guard

748
00:30:37,565 --> 00:30:38,485
at Ziyu Garden.

749
00:30:38,846 --> 00:30:39,606
Are you looking for a job?

750
00:30:45,285 --> 00:30:45,606
Sure.

751
00:30:45,966 --> 00:30:46,325
Really?

752
00:30:47,446 --> 00:30:47,725
Yeah.

753
00:30:48,525 --> 00:30:49,045
What job?

754
00:30:49,646 --> 00:30:51,446
New house cleanup.

755
00:30:51,446 --> 00:30:52,206
How about that?

756
00:30:52,325 --> 00:30:52,725
Can you do it?

757
00:30:56,285 --> 00:30:57,045
Yes.

758
00:30:59,606 --> 00:30:59,966
Mr. Yu,

759
00:31:00,565 --> 00:31:01,325
I've found the workers.

760
00:31:01,966 --> 00:31:02,846
They can help clear away

761
00:31:03,045 --> 00:31:03,886
the construction debris.

762
00:31:04,285 --> 00:31:05,166
And they're affordable

763
00:31:05,565 --> 00:31:05,926
and reliable.

764
00:31:11,005 --> 00:31:12,085
Awesome! Thank you!

765
00:31:12,285 --> 00:31:12,686
You're welcome.

766
00:31:13,200 --> 00:31:16,510
(Bridgeway Financial.
Need Cash Fast? Call Us.)

767
00:31:21,406 --> 00:31:21,846
Sorry.

768
00:31:31,325 --> 00:31:31,646
Yitong.

769
00:31:31,966 --> 00:31:32,406
You're back.

770
00:31:45,325 --> 00:31:45,966
You must be his wife?

771
00:31:47,166 --> 00:31:47,686
Who are you?

772
00:31:47,886 --> 00:31:48,325
Yu Ming.

773
00:31:48,525 --> 00:31:49,206
You're his wife, right?

774
00:31:50,245 --> 00:31:50,646
What's going on?

775
00:31:50,805 --> 00:31:51,846
We're from Bridgeway Financial.

776
00:31:53,206 --> 00:31:53,646
Um...

777
00:31:54,126 --> 00:31:54,966
Funds transferred.

778
00:31:55,325 --> 00:31:55,926
Our boss

779
00:31:56,045 --> 00:31:56,646
asked us to come over

780
00:31:57,245 --> 00:31:58,245
to do a property appraisal.

781
00:31:58,446 --> 00:31:58,966
What?

782
00:32:00,126 --> 00:32:01,446
A property appraisal.

783
00:32:03,085 --> 00:32:04,406
You just moved in, right?

784
00:32:04,966 --> 00:32:06,045
I'm your neighbor.

785
00:32:06,565 --> 00:32:08,366
This house is cursed.

786
00:32:08,725 --> 00:32:10,285
The first owner drowned in the sea.

787
00:32:10,406 --> 00:32:12,166
The second hanged himself from the beam.

788
00:32:12,966 --> 00:32:13,886
This house

789
00:32:14,366 --> 00:32:15,805
has been empty for years.

790
00:32:16,245 --> 00:32:17,725
One after another just comes and goes.

791
00:32:19,765 --> 00:32:22,846
They all got scared off by that thing
hanging from the chandelier.

792
00:32:26,285 --> 00:32:26,926
Can you feel it?

793
00:32:27,366 --> 00:32:28,406
That chill

794
00:32:28,525 --> 00:32:30,285
crawling up your spine?

795
00:32:30,285 --> 00:32:30,926
No.

796
00:32:31,085 --> 00:32:32,926
Didn't you hear it?

797
00:32:32,926 --> 00:32:34,606
Someone's blowing in your ear.

798
00:32:35,966 --> 00:32:37,485
Put me down!

799
00:32:37,606 --> 00:32:38,926
Put me down!

800
00:32:40,085 --> 00:32:40,725
Put me down?

801
00:32:40,846 --> 00:32:42,166
Wait. Didn't he kill himself?

802
00:32:42,485 --> 00:32:43,166
Kill himself?

803
00:32:43,285 --> 00:32:44,686
Even suicide can come with regret.

804
00:32:44,846 --> 00:32:45,686
Go ask around.

805
00:32:46,085 --> 00:32:47,045
Within ten miles,

806
00:32:47,045 --> 00:32:48,646
everyone knows this house is cursed.

807
00:32:48,886 --> 00:32:50,646
They wouldn't take the money for it.

808
00:32:50,886 --> 00:32:52,366
How come you bought it?

809
00:32:52,366 --> 00:32:53,886
Back then, I went home.

810
00:32:53,886 --> 00:32:54,886
My mother-in-law was here.

811
00:32:55,045 --> 00:32:55,686
She saw it.

812
00:32:55,846 --> 00:32:56,646
Saw what?

813
00:32:56,926 --> 00:32:59,406
He hung for days before anyone noticed.

814
00:32:59,565 --> 00:33:00,686
The window

815
00:33:00,805 --> 00:33:01,725
was wide open.

816
00:33:01,805 --> 00:33:02,805
The wind was strong.

817
00:33:02,805 --> 00:33:04,126
He looked like a big red sausage,

818
00:33:04,285 --> 00:33:05,085
swaying in the wind.

819
00:33:05,485 --> 00:33:06,606
By the time the coroner arrived,

820
00:33:06,886 --> 00:33:08,886
his skin was all swollen.

821
00:33:09,126 --> 00:33:09,805
As they walked in,

822
00:33:10,446 --> 00:33:12,485
his head and body were separate.

823
00:33:13,045 --> 00:33:14,206
Each one in a different place.

824
00:33:14,366 --> 00:33:15,005
You'd think

825
00:33:15,126 --> 00:33:15,886
his body

826
00:33:16,005 --> 00:33:16,686
was on the floor, right?

827
00:33:17,166 --> 00:33:17,325
No.

828
00:33:17,565 --> 00:33:19,045
It was sitting on the couch.

829
00:33:19,325 --> 00:33:19,926
And his head

830
00:33:20,325 --> 00:33:22,646
was still hanging on the chandelier.

831
00:33:22,686 --> 00:33:23,206
Scary, isn't it?

832
00:33:25,485 --> 00:33:26,045
Mr. Yu.

833
00:33:26,926 --> 00:33:27,325
Hello.

834
00:33:27,966 --> 00:33:29,725
I'm Jiang Xiaoling
from property management.

835
00:33:29,966 --> 00:33:31,045
You can just call me Jiang.

836
00:33:31,085 --> 00:33:31,846
Hello.

837
00:33:32,045 --> 00:33:33,126
This is also our staff.

838
00:33:33,166 --> 00:33:33,926
Hello.

839
00:33:34,245 --> 00:33:35,005
Are you planning

840
00:33:35,085 --> 00:33:36,565
to start renovations?

841
00:33:36,926 --> 00:33:38,565
Just doing some cleanup first.

842
00:33:38,725 --> 00:33:39,886
Here's the thing, Mr. Yu.

843
00:33:40,565 --> 00:33:41,446
The villa you bought,

844
00:33:41,446 --> 00:33:42,606
Unit 505,

845
00:33:42,606 --> 00:33:43,765
has unpaid property management fees

846
00:33:43,805 --> 00:33:44,485
and utility bills.

847
00:33:44,565 --> 00:33:45,606
So we can't issue

848
00:33:45,606 --> 00:33:47,285
a transport pass for trucks.

849
00:33:47,525 --> 00:33:48,606
Which means

850
00:33:48,646 --> 00:33:50,166
you can't remove renovation debris yet.

851
00:33:50,366 --> 00:33:51,765
Once you settle all fees,

852
00:33:51,926 --> 00:33:52,725
and get the pass,

853
00:33:52,846 --> 00:33:54,085
then renovations can begin.

854
00:33:54,846 --> 00:33:55,805
Here's our notice.

855
00:33:56,005 --> 00:33:56,966
Please sign it.

856
00:33:57,166 --> 00:33:59,206
Wait. I don't quite understand.

857
00:33:59,325 --> 00:33:59,765
To be clear,

858
00:34:00,126 --> 00:34:01,166
without the pass,

859
00:34:01,166 --> 00:34:02,325
we won't open the gate

860
00:34:02,325 --> 00:34:02,765
for trucks.

861
00:34:02,886 --> 00:34:04,285
So all this debris they're moving

862
00:34:04,406 --> 00:34:04,926
won't get out of

863
00:34:04,926 --> 00:34:05,446
the community.

864
00:34:05,446 --> 00:34:06,406
I haven't even moved in yet.

865
00:34:06,485 --> 00:34:07,606
I just got the keys.

866
00:34:07,606 --> 00:34:08,966
How could I possibly have those fees?

867
00:34:09,205 --> 00:34:11,525
Those were left behind

868
00:34:11,525 --> 00:34:12,286
by the owner before last.

869
00:34:12,525 --> 00:34:13,485
Altogether, it's about

870
00:34:13,645 --> 00:34:14,326
120,000.

871
00:34:14,525 --> 00:34:15,165
How much?

872
00:34:15,326 --> 00:34:15,966
120,000.

873
00:34:15,966 --> 00:34:17,165
